TITLE: Managing Event Listeners in Puppeteer
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to add and remove event listeners for page requests using Puppeteer's EventEmitter methods.
SOURCE: https://github.com/puppeteer/puppeteer/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-24.7.0/api/puppeteer.page.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
```
function logRequest(interceptedRequest) {
  console.log('A request was made:', interceptedRequest.url());
}
page.on('request', logRequest);
// Sometime later...
page.off('request', logRequest);
```

