## [22.0.0](https://github.com/puppeteer/puppeteer/compare/puppeteer-v21.11.0...puppeteer-v22.0.0) (2024-02-05)

###  BREAKING CHANGES

- rename createIncognitoBrowserContext to createBrowserContext
- enable the new-headless mode by default
- remove networkConditions in favor of PredefinedNetworkConditions
- use ReadableStreams
- remove duplicate type names
- remove add/removeEventListener in favor of on/off
- make console warn level compatible with WebDriver BiDi
- remove InterceptResolutionStrategy
- remove devices in favor of KnownDevices
- remove `$x` and `waitForXpath`
- remove waitForTimeout
- generate accessible PDFs by default
- remove `error` const, change CustomError to PuppeteerError
- remove viewport resizing from ElementHandle.screenshot
- remove PUPPETEER_DOWNLOAD_PATH in favor of PUPPETEER_CACHE_DIR
- BiDi cookies
- drop support for node16
```

